<h1><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>Sharing by Email</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-files"><i class="fa fa-share"></i>Sharing Files</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>Sharing by Email</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> allows you to share files and folders by email.  When sharing items by email, you can send files and folders as either email attachments or as a link. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>Sharing Items by Email</h2>
			<p>To share an item by email, select the file or folder that you would like to share and then click "By Email" on the Share menu. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="dropdown menu" src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-email/share-by-email-menu-item@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">"By Email" on the Share Menu</div>
			</div>

			<p>This will bring up the Share by Email dialog box where you can enter the email address of the recipient and your email message. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-email/share-by-email-dialog.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Share by Email Dialog"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-email/share-by-email-dialog.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Share by Email Dialog</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-link"></i>Sharing Items as Attachments</h2>
			<p>When you share items as attachments, the files and folders will be appended to the email as attachments. If folders are appended, they will be compressed first and attached as '.zip' files. </p>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-link"></i>Sharing Items as Links</h2>
			<p>When you select the Send as Link radio button, then a "Next" button will appear to allow you to enter additional link info. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-email/share-by-email-link.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Share by Email Link"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-email/share-by-email-link.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Share by Email Link</div>
			</div>

			<p>Pressing the "Next" button will allow you to enter optional link expiration and protection info.  When finished specifying this information, press "Send" to send the email containing a link to the specified file or folder along with your email message. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-email/share-by-email-link-info.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Share by Email Link Info"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-email/share-by-email-link-info.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Share by Email Link Info</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>